title: Overcast Map Collection
subtitle: A collection of publicly downloadable Minecraft maps from Overcast Network
body:
This map collection is no longer being maintained and may not work with the current version of PGM. Please refer to our PGM Collection for maintained maps.

This map collection was designed and tested to be used with Overcast's open source plugins (Project Ares) and we recommend using those to have the best experience with this map. This map may also include one of Overcast's standard XML files, which all can be found here to download. If you prefer to use the (maintained) 1.8 fork of Project Ares, you can find that here instead. Maps using the XML protocol 1.4.1 and above may not work and will have to be manually downgraded to at least protocol 1.4.0. Additionally, the Minecraft world will have to be converted to Minecraft version 1.8. This can be easily done using this NBT converter tool.
